	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Blacksmith</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		<div id="contentSub2"></div>
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#searchInput">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Blacksmith_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Blacksmith (disambiguation)">Blacksmith (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Blacksmiths" redirects here. For the suburb in New South Wales, see <a href="/wiki/Blacksmiths,_New_South_Wales" title="Blacksmiths, New South Wales">Blacksmiths, New South Wales</a>.</div>
